author: Sam J.
title: But RUSSIA! Conservative Review uses Hillary fanboy Peter Daou’s tweet against him, and it’s EPIC
text:
UGLY PANTSUITS. Quick word of advice to anyone who responds to Russian tampering with "Hillary didn't campaign in WI." Try harder. That talking point is old 
— Peter Daou (@peterdaou) February 21, 2017 
Gosh, Peter sounds fussy. And the age of the talking point is irrelevant, it’s true. Wisconsin cost her. 
God Bless Wisconsin. 
— Conservative Review (@CR) February 21, 2017 
OUCH. 
Heh. @CR So I take it Conservative Review is deflecting criticism of Russian tampering that our intel agencies confirmed by attacking Clinton? 
— Peter Daou (@peterdaou) February 21, 2017 
Waaaah. 
— Conservative Review (@CR) February 21, 2017 
Hey, it’s not Conservative Review’s fault if the facts don’t look good on Hillary.
